  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.poster.avif?t=1698204406\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.webm?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.mp4?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Waking up disoriented, confused, and detached from his usual senses, a person with the identification number “404” finds himself at the old treehouse that isn’t supposed to be there anymore. There are only two things left in his cloudy mind: a desire to paint and a mysterious attachment to this place with every single trivial object in it. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.poster.avif?t=1698204406\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.webm?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.mp4?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>✨ <strong>Key Features</strong> ✨<br>🖍  Relaxing retro pixel puzzles <br>🖍  A heartfelt story of self-discovery and hope<br>🖍  Nostalgic environment and music<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/55bc356ba706b96f45d56701a76d406e.poster.avif?t=1698204406\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/55bc356ba706b96f45d56701a76d406e.webm?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/55bc356ba706b96f45d56701a76d406e.mp4?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>          <i>Place the missing pieces into their designated spots and fill the void of one’s soul</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/897901a6aba8a2b963211589375bd27e.avif?t=1698204406\" width=650 height=210 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/f9f7c19abf66e18950f3074555c97fa6.avif?t=1698204406\" width=650 height=210 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.poster.avif?t=1698204406\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.webm?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/c989b9b683aa147db24d63e115fcb63a.mp4?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Waking up disoriented, confused, and detached from his usual senses, a person with the identification number “404” finds himself at the old treehouse that isn’t supposed to be there anymore. There are only two things left in his cloudy mind: a desire to paint and a mysterious attachment to this place with every single trivial object in it. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.poster.avif?t=1698204406\" width=616 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.webm?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/215ccdd0064c7cf9876635ff5f012d06.mp4?t=1698204406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>✨ <strong>Key Features</strong> ✨<br>🖍  Relaxing retro pixel puzzles <br>🖍  A heartfelt story of self-discovery and hope<br>🖍  Nostalgic environment and music<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2586500/extras/55bc356ba706b96f45d56701a76d406e.poster